@startuml seq_08_browse_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-08 Browse Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "Post Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open forum homepage
Frontend -> Controller: (2.1) GET /api/posts/public-feed
Controller -> Service: (2.2) Load and fetch public posts
Service -> Redis: (2.3) Check cache for feed
alt Cache Hit
    Redis --> Service: (2.4) Cached feed data
else Cache Miss
    Redis --> Service: (2.5) Null
    Service -> Repo: (2.6) Fetch recent public posts
    Repo --> Service: (2.7) List of posts
    Service -> Redis: (2.8) Store feed in cache (TTL)
end
Service --> Controller: (3.1/4.1) Feed data
Controller --> Frontend: (3.2/4.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (3.3/4.3) Display post list or empty state

User -> Frontend: (5.1) Select a post
Frontend -> Controller: (5.2) GET /api/posts/{post_id}
Controller -> Service: (6.1) Fetch selected post details
Service -> Repo: (6.2) Fetch post by ID
Repo --> Service: (6.3) Post details
Service --> Controller: (7.1) Post details
Controller --> Frontend: (7.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (7.3) Display full post content
@enduml
